      "work_item_kind": "review_defect",
      "issue_kind": "review_defect",
      "origin": "review_import",
      "note": "Replaced four falsy guards in src/routes/api/browse-logs/+server.ts with explicit null checks: log.encounter_id != null ?, log.duration_ms != null ?, row.lastUpdated != null ?, and start_time/end_time using ?? 0. duration_ms and similar can legitimately be 0 (very short fight or boundary case); the prior '? :' / '|| 0' would have collapsed those to the fallback path, hiding the value. Behavior is preserved for genuine null/undefined while no longer corrupting zero. svelte-check still 0 errors. Commit pushed.",
      "first_seen": "2026-04-26T07:42:20+00:00",
